article.description: — Souley Boum scored 23 points as UTEP beat McNeese State 82-72 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Boum leads UTEP past McNeese St. 82-72
article.linkText: Boum leads UTEP past McNeese St. 82-72
article.story: EL PASO, Texas -- — Souley Boum scored 23 points as UTEP beat McNeese State 82-72 on Thursday night. Keonte Kennedy added 20 points for the Miners. Jorell Saterfield had 13 points for UTEP (6-4). Collin Warren had 13 points for the Cowboys (3-8), whose losing streak reached five games. Myles Lewis added 10 points. Brendan Medley-Bacon had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
